column5: Caught the biggest perch I've ever seen today in Orillia. Thought for sure it was a bass until it surfaced. 14+ inches! and a huge girth. Took a bunch of pictures and I'm going to get a Replica made. She was released alive and well too grow even bigger!  I've set the bar high for any other Teams that want too mess with Team #5
That is a fattie.....Congrats man  Cheers  Craig
I want to see that perch beside a tape measure and a pic where it's not extended away from your body...just messing with ya, what a hog.
Awesome !!! Whats going on recently !? Are the waterways being taken over by huge killer perch
Good genes in that broad.  Glad you released her
Even if I did want too eat her, wouldn't it be like leather...
Great catch!   And no, it would be delicious.  That sure is a nice perch man. Congrats.
Great catch and good on you for c+r I also caught my biggest perch today, at a scrappy 12".
Congrats on your PB perch! Jumbo for sure!
TOUCHE!   Awewsome stuff Shawn.....congrats on the PB!  Great contribution to this years winning total!
